OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776438666
OL,3,CBrother of murder accused doused in
OL,4,Cboiling water in court
OL,6,FA man was left with serious burn
OL,7,Finjuries after boiling water was
OL,8,Fthrown over him in a Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fcourthouse.
OL,11,FIt is understood the attacker was
OL,12,Fcarrying a kettle which had been
OL,13,Fboiled elsewhere in Strabane's
OL,14,Fcourthouse.
OL,16,FThe man injured is understood to be a
OL,17,Fbrother of murder accused Dylan
OL,18,FMcCrossan, 32, from Beechmount
OL,19,FVillage, Strabane.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
