CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776438666
OL,3,CBrother of murder accused doused in
OL,4,Cboiling water in court
OL,6,FBoth men are brothers of SDLP West
OL,7,FTyrone MLA Daniel McCrossan.
OL,9,FDylan McCrossan is accused of the
OL,10,Fmurder of Stephen Holmes.
OL,12,FMr Holmes, 31, died at the Royal
OL,13,FVictoria Hospital in Belfast as a
OL,14,Fresult of the severe injuries he
OL,15,Fsustained following a brutal assault
OL,16,Fin the Beechmount Village area of
OL,17,FStrabane.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776438666
OL,3,CBrother of murder accused doused in
OL,4,Cboiling water in court
OL,6,FOn Thursday, as a committal hearing to
OL,7,Ftransfer the case for trial was due to
OL,8,Ftake place, a scuffle broke out at the
OL,9,Frear of the court causing District
OL,10,FJudge Alana McSorley to immediately
OL,11,Fhalt proceedings.
OL,13,FSeconds later a court official dashed
OL,14,Finto the courtroom and grabbed a jug
OL,15,Fof water from one of the benches and
OL,16,Frushed back out.
OL,18,FThis was used to cool the wounded
OL,19,Fman's injuries while awaiting an
OL,20,Fambulance.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776438666
OL,3,CBrother of murder accused doused in
OL,4,Cboiling water in court
OL,6,FHe was taken to hospital for treatment
OL,7,Fto burns on his face, neck and
OL,8,Fshoulder.
OL,10,FAround two hours later the court
OL,11,Fresumed but Judge McSorley said
OL,12,Ffollowing consultation with the Office
OL,13,Fof the Lady Chief Justice in view of
OL,14,Fwhat has occurred, in court the
OL,15,Fcommittal was adjourned until May 14.
OL,17,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "Police
OL,18,Fresponded to an incident at Strabane
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court at which has left a
OL,20,Fman injured and requiring hospital
OL,21,Ftreatment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
