OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776438666
OL,3,CBrother of murder accused doused in
OL,4,Cboiling water in court
OL,6,F"At 10.52am it was reported a man had
OL,7,Fthrown hot water over another man,
OL,8,Fcausing burn injuries to his face and
OL,9,Fupper body. NI Ambulance Service also
OL,10,Fresponded and took the victim to
OL,11,Fhospital for treatment."
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Ballentine said:
OL,14,F"The suspect is reported to have run
OL,15,Faway from the scene, and police
OL,16,Fefforts are ongoing to identify,
OL,17,Flocate and apprehend the suspect.
OL,19,F"We are liaising with Northern Ireland
OL,20,FCourts and Tribunals Service regards
OL,21,Fthis incident."
OL,26,@{D@AOU
